<p>According to <a href="https://www.ziprecruiter.com/Salaries/Seo-Freelancer-Salary">ZipRecruiter data for April 2026</a>, the average SEO freelancer in the United States earns $54.49 per hour or roughly $113,333 per year. <a href="https://seranking.com/blog/freelance-vs-in-house-seo-salary/">SE Ranking reports</a> that freelance SEOs out-earn in-house SEO specialists by 14.4 percent at the median, and nearly 14 percent of freelancers earn over $150,000 per year.</p>
